title: Best Yogurt Ever
review: I hope they NEVER ever change the recipe for this yogurt. I grew up on real full fat yogurt and in America couldn’t find anything that tasted good. But this French yogurt hits the spot! They truly brought French yogurt to America. It’s pure dairy goodness.

title: Best yogurt

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2019
name: Christy G
title: The best yogurt I’ve ever had!
review: Unbelievably good! We love all 3 flavors, especially with Michele’s granola on top! It’s thick like custard, and does not seem to upset my hubby’s lactose intolerant tummy for some reason. The little jars are glazed terra cotta & I have re-used them as pen cups. Now I send them to my sister, who makes cool craft things from them! Would be great for votive candles or succulents.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2019
name: Fresia Moore
title: Perfect Pampering in a ceramic Pot
review: Well, they sent me to Wholefoods to buy yogurt. “Buy something interesting,” they said. There I picked this one and a few others. Of all the ones I picked this one was the best!!! So rich! So delicious! So satisfying! So decadent! I’ll be buying more. The glass containers will be in my cupboard. They are like ceramic pottery. It would be a shame to throw them away. It’s such a lovely eating experience and well worth the money. Try it you will love yourself for the pamper.
